author: Brianne Tolj
title: Fake MDMA sweeps Canberra | Daily Mail Online
text: Woman fighting for her life after taking ‘bad batch of MDMA’ – a month after 20 partygoers were hospitalised with similar drug Canberra woman is in hospital after she took what she believed to be MDMA She began having seizures and would've died without medical help, doctor said It is believed the bad batch of drugs was similar to that found in Melbourne Three people died in Melbourne last month after taking related batch of drugs 20 people who were partying on Chapel Street were rushed to hospital Published: 06:04 GMT, 24 February 2017 | Updated: 08:21 GMT, 24 February 2017 69 shares
